<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>105</hymn_number>
<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
<aka>This gospel of the kingdom shall first be preached in all the world and then the end shall come.</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs holitopa ʋba Mi̱ko yʋt
 Okla puta moma ka i̱ hullo hosh,
 &quot;Ʋbanumpa hanta ihi̱ma la he,&quot;
 Achi tok oka, pi yukpa fehnʋshke.

[V2]
 &quot;Ʋm anumpa hʋt yakni moma hoka
 Ayʋt hlopullit a taiyahakmak o̱,
 Nitak ishtaiyopi ʋla hi oke,&quot;
 Ahanchi pulla tok a̱, pi yimmishke.

[V3]
 Hatak ithana puta hʋchia ma!
 Ʋba anumpa ilʋppa fehna kʋt
 Yakni a̱ hlopullit maha̱ya hoka,
 Yʋmmak a hi atuk ʋt ai a̱hlishke.

[V4]
 Chisʋs im anumpa ilʋppak okʋt
 Oklushi moyuma ka im ona cha,
 Ai anuhumpa na, ha̱klot yimmi hosh,
 Chihowa immi tokʋt okcha̱yashke.</lyrics>
<title>Chisʋs holitopa ʋba Mi̱ko yʋ ƲIT105</title>
<time_sig>11.11.11.11.</time_sig>
</song>